A simple game of life implementation.
To run the game, compile the sources with the following commands:
gcc -o gol gol.c
Then run the program with the following comamnd:
./gol 50

/!\ (You may need to set the execute permission to run the program (chmod '+x' gol) /!\

The following options are availables:
./gol [line_size][columns_size][update_time][init_cells_apparition_percent] (the minimal size is 5 and the maximum percent is 100)
